	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="edition">
				<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
					<ab>
						<title>
							<supplied reason="lost">Esther 8</supplied>
						</title>
						<milestone unit="line" n="13"/>
						<l n="1" xml:id="Est-008-001"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ביום</foreign>Ol künd́a berdi ol bij Aḥašveroš Es-
							<milestone unit="line" n="14"/>terǵa ol bijč́aǵa ošol üvün Hamannyn tar berüv-
							<milestone unit="line" n="15"/>čüsünün ol Jisraʾelĺarnin da Mardeḫaj keldi alnyna
							<milestone unit="line" n="16"/>ol bijnin ki anlatty Ester nečik uruvdu ol anar.
						</l>
						<milestone unit="line" n="17"/>
						<l n="2" xml:id="Est-008-002"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויסר</foreign> Da ket́ardi ol bij ošol mohorlu jüzügün
							<milestone unit="line" n="18"/>ki ašyrdy Hamandan da berdi any Mardeḫajɣa da
							<milestone unit="line" n="19"/>qojdu Ester ošol Mardeḫajny aɣaraq üvü üstüńa
							<milestone unit="line" n="20"/>Hamannyn.
						</l>
						<l n="3" xml:id="Est-008-003"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותוסף</foreign> Da arttyrdy Ester da sözĺa<supplied reason="lost">di</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="21"/>alnynda ol bijnin da tüštü ajaqlary üstüńa 
							<supplied reason="lost">anyn</supplied>
							<milestone unit="page" n="382v" facs="ADub.III.73.382v.jpg"/>
							<milestone unit="line" n="1"/>da jylady da jalbardy anar ašyrma ošol jamanlyɣyn
							<milestone unit="line" n="2"/>Hamannyn ol Agaglynyn da ošol jaman saɣyšyn anyn ki
							<milestone unit="line" n="3"/>saɣyš etti ol Jisraʾelĺar üstüńa.
						</l>
						<l n="4" xml:id="Est-008-004"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויושט
							</foreign><milestone unit="line" n="4"/>Da burɣady ol bij Esterg’a ošol ol altyn čybuq-
							<milestone unit="line" n="5"/>nu da turdu Ester da toḥtady alnynda ol bijnin.
						</l>
						<milestone unit="line" n="6"/>
						<l n="5" xml:id="Est-008-005"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותאמר</foreign> Da ajtty Ester eger ol bijǵa jaḥšy
							<milestone unit="line" n="7"/>körünśa da eger taptym širinlik alnyn-
							<milestone unit="line" n="8"/>da anyn da qolajlyq eśa ol söz alnynda ol bijnin da
							<milestone unit="line" n="9"/>jaḥšy eśam men közĺarind́a anyn jazylsyn qajtarma
							<milestone unit="line" n="10"/>ošol ol bitikĺarni saɣyšyn Hamannyn uvlunun ol Meda-
							<milestone unit="line" n="11"/>tanyn ol Agaglynyn ki jazdy tasetḿa ošol ol Jisra-
							<milestone unit="line" n="12"/>ʾelĺarni ki bar valajatlarynda ol bijnin.
						</l>
						<l n="6" xml:id="Est-008-006"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי</foreign> Ki nečik
							<milestone unit="line" n="13"/>bolalyrmen ki körǵajmen jamanny ki učrar ošol ulusum-
							<milestone unit="line" n="14"/>nu da nečik bolalyrmen ki körǵajmen ki taspolmaɣyn tuv-
							<milestone unit="line" n="15"/>mušumnun.
						</l>
						<l n="7" xml:id="Est-008-007"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign> Da ajtty ol bij Aḥašveroš
							<milestone unit="line" n="16"/>Ester ol bijč́aǵa da Mardeḫajǵa ol Jisraʾelǵa
							<milestone unit="line" n="17"/>muna üvün Hamannyn berdim Esterǵa da any as-
							<milestone unit="line" n="18"/>tylar ol asqyč üstüńa anyn üčün ki kĺadi sun-
							<milestone unit="line" n="19"/>ma qolun Jisraʾelĺar üstüńa.
						</l>
						<l n="8" xml:id="Est-008-008"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואתם</foreign> Da
							<milestone unit="line" n="20"/>biz jazyjyz ol Jisraʾelĺarǵa nečik jaḥšy körünś́a köz-
							<milestone unit="line" n="21"/>ĺarijizd́a aty byla ol bijnin da mohorlajiz mohorlu
							<milestone unit="page" n="383r" facs="ADub.III.73.383r.jpg"/>
							<milestone unit="line" n="1"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">jüzü</supplied>gü byla ol bijnin ki bitik ki jazylsa <seg type="commented" corresp="#Est-008-seg001"/>aty
							<supplied reason="lost">byla ol</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="2"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">bij</supplied>nin<anchor type="commented" xml:id="Est-008-seg001"/> da mohorlansa mohoru byla ol bijnin <seg type="commented" corresp="#Est-008-seg002"/>uša
							<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>a
							<supplied reason="lost">jdy</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="3"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">boš</supplied> qajtarma<anchor type="commented" xml:id="Est-008-seg002"/>.
						</l>
						<l n="9" xml:id="Est-008-009"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקראו</foreign> Da ünd́aldilar jazuvč
							<supplied reason="lost">ulary</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="4"/>ol bijnin ol vaḥtta ol üčünčü janɣajda 
							<supplied reason="lost">ol-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="5"/>du janɣajy sivannyn igirmi üčünčü kününd́a a
							<supplied reason="lost">j-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="6"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">ny</supplied>n da jazyldy barča nečik ki bujurdu Mardeḫaj ol Jis
							<supplied reason="lost">ra-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="7"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">ʾe</supplied>lĺarǵa da ol özd́an bijĺarǵa da ol aɣalyqlar
							<supplied reason="lost">ɣa</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="8"/>da aɣaraqlaryna ol valajatlarnyn ki Hodudan da Kuš
							<supplied reason="lost">qa-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="9"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">de</supplied>jin jüz igirmi jedi valajat har valajatqa jazyšyna
							<milestone unit="line" n="10"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">k</supplied>öŕa da har ulusqa tilińa köŕa da ol Jisraʾe
							<supplied reason="lost">l-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="11"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">ĺar</supplied>ǵa jazyšlaryna köŕa da tilĺarińa köŕa.
							<milestone unit="line" n="12"/><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויכתב</foreign> Da jazdy Mardeḫaj aty była ol bijnin Aḥa
							<supplied reason="lost">š-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="13"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">ver</supplied>ošnun da mohorlady mohoru byla ol bijnin da
							<milestone unit="line" n="14"/>ijdi 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-008-add001" status="unremarkable"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">bitikĺar</supplied>
							<anchor xml:id="Est-008-add001" type="addSpan"/> qolu ašyra ol jeĺančiĺarnin atlar byla <seg type="commented" corresp="#Est-008-seg003"/>a
							<supplied reason="lost">tla-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="15"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>uvču<anchor type="commented" xml:id="Est-008-seg003"/> ol qatyr üstüńa ol eki ǯynslarda
							<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="16"/>ol ramak balalary üstüńa.
						</l>
						<l n="11" xml:id="Est-008-011"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אשר</foreign>Ki erk ber
							<supplied reason="lost">di</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="17"/>ol bij Jisraʾelĺarǵa ki har šaharda jyštyrylma da
							<milestone unit="line" n="18"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>urma ǯanlary üčün tasetḿa qyrma da joq e
							<supplied reason="lost">t-</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="19"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>’a ošol bar čerüvün ulusnun da valajatnyn ol t<supplied reason="lost">ar</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="20"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">be</supplied>rüvčuĺarnin alarɣa jašny da qatynlarny da malla<supplied reason="lost">rny</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="21"/>alarnyn talama.
						</l>
						<l n="12" xml:id="Est-008-012"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ביום</foreign> Bir küńd́a bar valajatlaryn
							<supplied reason="lost">da</supplied>
							<milestone unit="page" n="383v" facs="ADub.III.73.383v.jpg" />
							<milestone unit="line" n="1"/>ol bijnin Aḥašverošnun on üčünčü kü
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-008-add002" status="unremarkable"/>nü
							<anchor xml:id="Est-008-add002" type="addSpan"/>nde ol on eki<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>-
							<milestone unit="line" n="2"/>či janɣajnyn ol janɣajy adarnyn.
						</l>
						<l n="13" xml:id="Est-008-013"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פתשן</foreign> Kopijasy o<supplied reason="lost">l</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="3"/>bitiknin berilḿa qadaɣa har valajatta aškara bar ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="4"/>uluslarɣa da bolma ol Jisraʾlĺar hadi<addSpan spanTo="#Est-008-add003" status="unremarkable"/>r<anchor xml:id="Est-008-add003" type="addSpan"/>ĺar ošpu kün-
							<milestone unit="line" n="5"/>ǵa öč alma dušmanlaryndan özĺarinin.
						</l>
						<l n="14" xml:id="Est-008-014"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הרצים</foreign> 
						Ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="6"/>jeĺančiĺar atlanuvčular ol qatyr üstüńa ol eki ǯyn
							<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>-
							<milestone unit="line" n="7"/>lardan čyqtylar ašyɣa bušuɣa sözü byla ol bijnin da
							<milestone unit="line" n="8"/>ol qadaɣa berildi Šušan ol sarajda.
						</l>
						<l n="15" xml:id="Est-008-015"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ומרדכי</foreign> Da
							<milestone unit="line" n="9"/>Mardeḫaj čykty alnyndan ol bijnin bijlik upraq ičińa kök
							<milestone unit="line" n="10"/>da aq da altyn taǯ ullu bašy üstüńa anyn da plašč
							<milestone unit="line" n="11"/>keśajd́an da jipkind́an da ol šahar šahary Šušannyn bijandi
							<milestone unit="line" n="12"/>da quvandy.
						</l>
						<l n="16" xml:id="Est-008-016"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ליהודים</foreign>Jisraʾelĺarǵa boldu jaryqlyq da
							<milestone unit="line" n="13"/>bijanč da quvanč da abajlyq.
						</l>
						<l n="17" xml:id="Est-008-017"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובכל</foreign> Da har valajatta
							<milestone unit="line" n="14"/>da har šaharda ne orunda ki sözü ol bijnin da
							<milestone unit="line" n="15"/>qadaɣasy anyn jet́aredi bijanč da quvanč edi Jisraʾelĺarǵa
							<milestone unit="line" n="16"/>ički da šatyr kün da köpĺar uluslaryndan ol jerĺar-
							<milestone unit="line" n="17"/>nin Jisraʾel bolurediĺar 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-008-add004" status="unremarkable"/>ki<anchor xml:id="Est-008-add004" type="addSpan"/> tüštü qorquvu <delSpan  spanTo="#Est-008-del001">Mardeḫajnyn</delSpan>
							
							<anchor  xml:id="Est-008-del001" type="delSpan"/>			 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-008-add005" status="unremarkable"/>Jisraʾellernin<anchor xml:id="Est-008-add005" type="addSpan"/> alar
							<milestone unit="line" n="18"/>üstüńa.
						</l>
					</ab>
				</div>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
